        "name": "Siege Weapons (Environment Change)",
        "img": "icons/environment/settlement/city-gate.webp",
        "systemPath": "actions",
        "description": "<p>Consequence Countdown (6). The attacking force deploys siege weapons to try to raze the defenders’ fortifications. Activate the countdown when the siege begins (for a protracted siege, make this a long-term countdown instead). When it triggers, the defenders’ fortifications have been breached and the attackers flood inside.</p><p>You gain 2 Fear, then shift to the Pitched Battle environment and spotlight it.</p><p><em>What siege weapons are being deployed? Are they magical\u001c mundane\u001c or a mixture of both? What defenses must the characters overcome to storm the castle?</em></p>",
