        "img": "icons/environment/settlement/city-gate.webp",
        "systemPath": "actions",
        "description": "<p>When an adversary is defeated, you can spend a Fear to have a stray attack from a siege weapon hit a point on the battlefield. All targets within Very Close range of that point must make an Agility Reaction Roll.</p><p>• Targets who fail take [[3d8+3]] physical or magic damage and must mark a Stress.</p><p>• Targets who succeed must mark a Stress.</p><p><em>What debris is scattered by the attack? What is broken by the strike that can’t be easily mended?</em></p>",
